						<div class="postbody">CHR RAM on Neo Geo MVS/AES is &quot;possible&quot; in the same way that a grainy approximation of GameCube graphics on an NES is &quot;possible&quot; through a TV tuner that outputs CHR data. It's possible in theory but probably too expensive to bother.</div>

